2272  {
2273  enum _enumType : uint8_t
2274  {
2275  NONE = 0x00,
2276  DUAL_ANTENNA = 0x01,
2277  KINEMATIC = 0x02,
2278  MAGNETOMETER = 0x04,
2279  ALL = 0x07,
2280  };
2281  uint8_t value = NONE;
2282 
2283  AlignmentSelector() : value(NONE) {}
2284  AlignmentSelector(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
2285  operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
2286  AlignmentSelector& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
2287  AlignmentSelector& operator=(int val) { value = val; return *this; }
2288  AlignmentSelector& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
2289  AlignmentSelector& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
2290 
2291  bool dualAntenna() const { return (value & DUAL_ANTENNA) > 0; }
2292  void dualAntenna(bool val) { if(val) value |= DUAL_ANTENNA; else value &= ~DUAL_ANTENNA; }
2293  bool kinematic() const { return (value & KINEMATIC) > 0; }
2294  void kinematic(bool val) { if(val) value |= KINEMATIC; else value &= ~KINEMATIC; }
2295  bool magnetometer() const { return (value & MAGNETOMETER) > 0; }
2296  void magnetometer(bool val) { if(val) value |= MAGNETOMETER; else value &= ~MAGNETOMETER; }
2297 
2298  bool allSet() const { return value == ALL; }
2299  void setAll() { value |= ALL; }
2300  };
